--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
INFORMATION
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This file lists changes made to the Ansible role. It follows semantic versioning
guidelines. The content is sorted in reverse chronological order and formatted
to allow easy grepping by scripts.

The fields are:
B: bug
C: change
E: enhancement
F: feature

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

* Version 2.0.0 (2020-06-29)
C: Redesign role to support SELinux

* Version 1.2.2 (2020-01-08)
B: Minor Jinja2 statement fix

* Version 1.2.1 (2019-10-24)
B: Remove conflicting package task before configuring proxy and repositories

* Version 1.2.0 (2019-05-26)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.8

* Version 1.1.0 (2019-03-08)
F: Add 'yum_check-update' script

* Version 1.0.2 (2018-12-12)
B: Remove 'yum_name_default' parameter remainings
E: Minor Jinja2 style improvement

* Version 1.0.1 (2018-12-12)
E: Minor Jinja2 style improvement

* Version 1.0.0 (2018-12-12)
E: Mark Ansible role as 'stable'
E: Minor style improvement
E: Rename config parameters

* Version 0.3.1 (2018-11-26)
E: Minor style correction

* Version 0.3.0 (2018-05-21)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.5

* Version 0.2.2 (2018-04-24)
E: Simplify role by removing 'template' option

* Version 0.2.1 (2018-04-19)
E: Change default URL for EPEL repositories

* Version 0.2.0 (2018-03-30)
F: Port role to Ansible 2.4

* Version 0.1.1 (2018-02-16)
F: Fix multiple variable names

* Version 0.1.0 (2018-01-25)
F: Initial release
